# myPKA Cockpit — root .gitignore
# This folder is copied INTO a user's myPKA scaffold at
# <scaffold-root>/Expansions/mypka-cockpit/ and then uploaded to GitHub.
# Everything below is either regenerable, runtime state, or a secret.

# --- Dependencies & build output (regenerable; rebuilt on first run) ---------
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
web/node_modules/
**/dist/
web/dist/
web/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Live SQLite state (personal runtime data — never source) ----------------
*.db
*.db-*
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
mypka-cockpit.db*

# --- Secrets — never commit. Ship only the template (.env.example). ----------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Self-hosted basemap archive (regenerable; see web/public/basemap) -------
*.pmtiles

# --- Transients & caches -----------------------------------------------------
*.log
route-cache/
**/route-cache/
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# --- Local runtime write-audit & per-click hand-off notes --------------------
workbench-audit/
.assistant-request.md
.discuss-request.md

# --- Release packages produced locally — never commit ------------------------
dist-release/
